We ve added an Online Help Center to help you quickly find answers to questions about the mobile app! If you don t find an answer to your question in the Help Center please contact us by email karaokesupport stingray.com so that we may ensure your karaoke experience is the best!

We ve added a swim lane to display the free songs so that they re easy to find quickly. We ve fixed a few iOS 13 issues and have improved stability of the app. We ve also added a lot of songs recently and will continue to add more. Be sure to come back every week to sing the new songs! Please update the app and if you like it please rate the app and leave us a review in the App Store. If you have questions or need help using the app please contact us at karaokesupport stingray.com we d love to help you enjoy singing karaoke with your Singing Machine!

You can now register your Singing Machine using the mobile app! Register your machine when you create your account or by navigating to Account and Settings. Be sure to register your Singing Machine to take advantage of special offers that your machine may be eligible for. Please update and enjoy singing karaoke today! We d love to hear your feedback. Please send us an email at karaokesupport stingray.com with any comments or questions you have about the Singing Machine Karaoke app. Thanks for updating!

We ve fixed a bug that was causing a crash. Please update to enjoy an improved experience. We d love to hear your feedback about the Singing Machine Karaoke app. Please send comments or questions by email to karaokesupport stingray.com Thanks!

This update: fixes an in app subscription bug that was preventing a few customers from accessing full length songs. improves performance when browsing categories on the home page. Please update to improve your experience singing along with the Singing Machine karaoke app. If you experience any issues or would like to provide us feedback about the Singing Machine karaoke app please let us know by email at karaokesupport stingray.com.

Thanks for using the Singing Machine Karaoke App. This update includes stability improvements. Please update the app to ensure you enjoy the best karaoke experience. If you encounter any issues using the app please contact us by email karaokesupport stingray.com.

What s new: Facebook Login updated to support most recent Facebook App release Fixed bugs to improve stability Added In App Subscription information Thank you for updating. If you have comments or questions please email karaokesupport stingray.com or use the Contact Us form in the app.

New layout and design: easily access Showcase Recently Added Most Popular Songs Artists and more Song Queue: queue up to 100 songs to keep the karaoke party going Party Mixes: add thematic curated song lists to your song queue Save and access your favorite songs and song list history New Weekly In App subscription Karaoke Store: play songs purchased at the Karaoke Store. Thank you for updating. If you have comments or questions please email karaokesupport stingray.com or use the Contact Us form in the app.
